Given an iterable of actions, return a mapping of action groups.

actions: {'ec2:authorizesecuritygroupingress', 'iam:putrolepolicy', 'iam:listroles'}

Returns:
    {
        'ec2': {'Write'},
        'iam': {'Permissions', 'List'})
    }

Extracts all principals from IAM statement.

Should handle these cases:
"Principal": "value"
"Principal": ["value"]
"Principal": { "AWS": "value" }
"Principal": { "AWS": ["value", "value"] }
"Principal": { "Service": "value" }
"Principal": { "Service": ["value", "value"] }

Return: Set of principals
